### ==== MASTER DATA API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base route: /api/v1/masterdata
# Province/District/Ward — served from IMemoryCache (sub-1ms, AllowAnonymous)
# AdminUnits — IMemoryCache NeverRemove (AllowAnonymous)
# CaseType/JobTitle — OutputCache 30min (Authenticated)

# ── Province / District / Ward ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all active provinces
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/provinces

###

### List districts for a province
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/provinces/01/districts

###

### List wards for a district
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/provinces/01/districts/001/wards

# ── Administrative Units ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get admin units at level 1 (root)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/admin-units?level=1

###

### Get admin units at level 2 under a parent
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/admin-units?level=2&parentCode=VN

###

### Resolve successor for a merged/renamed admin unit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/admin-units/568/successor

# ── Case Types ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all active case types (global + tenant-scoped)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/case-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List case types for a specific tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/case-types?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Job Titles ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all active job titles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/job-titles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List job titles for a specific tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/masterdata/job-titles?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
